INSERT INTO wp_posts VALUES("319","1","2014-10-06 14:51:31","2014-10-06 14:51:31","<h1 class=\"brand-color workstream-h1 lighttext\">Workstream Structure</h1>\r\nInitially the Working Together programme has been constructed around 4 interdependent themes: Sharing and Adopting Good Practice, Developing a Sustainable Service Configuration, Assuring Sustainable Service Quality and creating a cross Trust care environment through the deployment of Informatics. The overall aim is to improve and sustain the quality of our clinical services whilst also providing them more efficiently and effectively and to do so together.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://inch-reform.codio.io:3000/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/structure_2.png\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-309 size-full\" src=\"http://inch-reform.codio.io:3000/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/structure_2.png\" alt=\"structure_2\" width=\"854\" height=\"506\" /></a>\r\n<h3>Workstream Projects</h3>\r\nEach workstream centres on commonly faced issues and aims. Each workstream has major colloborative projects and assigned Chief Executive leads, project management team and where applicable clinical leads. To find more information on each workstream, and the current projects, see the dedicated pages below:\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"media-list main-list\">\r\n          \r\n           <li class=\"media lighttext blockpadding rotherhambrand\">\r\n              <a class=\"media-heading lighttext\" href=\"http://inch-reform.codio.io:3000/wordpress/workstreams/sustainable-service-configuration/\">Sustainable Service Configuration</a>\r\n            </li>\r\n            \r\n           <li class=\"media lighttext blockpadding barnsleybrand\">\r\n              <a class=\"media-heading lighttext\" href=\"http://inch-reform.codio.io:3000/wordpress/workstreams/sustainable-care-quality/\">Sustainable Care Quality</a>\r\n           </li>   \r\n            \r\n           <li class=\"media lighttext blockpadding sheffchildbrand\">\r\n              <a class=\"media-heading lighttext\" href=\"http://inch-reform.codio.io:3000/wordpress/workstreams/sharing-and-adopting-good-practices/\">Sharing and adopting Good Practice</a>\r\n            </li>\r\n\r\n           <li class=\"media lighttext blockpadding sthbrand\">\r\n              <a class=\"media-heading lighttext\" href=\"http://inch-reform.codio.io:3000/wordpress/workstreams/informatics/\">Informatics</a>\r\n            </li>\r\n\r\n          </ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>For more information</h3>\r\nThe workstream groups are just beginning to formulate their plans and further updates will be circulated at regular intervals. For more information, or if you are interested in getting involved, please contact <a href=\"mailto:janettewatkins@nhs.net\">Janette Watkins (Programme Manager) via email</a> or by telephone on 01709 424 534.","Workstreams","","inherit","closed","open","","8-revision-v1","","","2014-10-06 14:51:31","2014-10-06 14:51:31","","8","http://inch-reform.codio.io:3000/wordpress/8-revision-v1/","0","revision","","0");
