ay-services/\">Project - Seven Day Services</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n	<li class=\"media lighttext blockpadding sheffchildbrand\"><a class=\"media-heading lighttext\" href=\"http://inch-reform.codio.io:3000/wordpress/workstreams/sharing-and-adopting-good-practices/\">Sharing and adopting Good Practice</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>For more information</h3>\r\nThe workstream groups are just beginning to formulate their plans and further updates will be circulated at regular intervals. For more information, or if you are interested in getting involved, please contact <a href=\"mailto:janettewatkins@nhs.net\">Janette Watkins (Programme Manager) via email</a> or by telephone on 01709 424 534.","Workstreams","","inherit","closed","open","","8-revision-v1","","","2014-10-13 10:34:06","2014-10-13 10:34:06","","8","http://inch-reform.codio.io:3000/wordpress/8-revision-v1/","0","revision","","0");
